                    <span>I liked this book for its simplicity. This book covers the ASP.NET controls from the data-driven applications perspective only and did the best job that can be done at it. Simple, precise and examples driven and gives you the understanding about the ASP.NET controls that you need. <p>A great book for a beginners and good reference for an intermediate ASP.NET programmers.</span>
                  
