                    <span>This would be a book I would recommend for novice ASP programmers or even new to web programmers. It was written with a bit fluff here and there greatly lacking concision I have come to demand from technical books. It did serve as a good overview book on ASP.Net and ADO.Net techniques but not much deeper than that.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">excellent coverage of fundamentals</div>
